ActYouth Criminal Justice Act
SubjectAGREEMENTS - Youth Criminal Justice Act
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Justice to enter into AGREEMENTS with the governments of the provinces and territories in order to financially assist the provinces and territories in their delivery of a range of youth justice services and programs that are consistent with federal policy objectives.
